sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant DeviceA
    participant DeviceB
    participant Cloud

    User->>DeviceA: Initiate Backup
    DeviceA->>Cloud: Upload Backup Data
    Cloud-->>DeviceA: Confirm Backup Completion

    User->>DeviceA: Initiate Restore
    DeviceA->>Cloud: Request Backup Data
    Cloud-->>DeviceA: Send Backup Data
    DeviceA-->>User: Restore Complete

    User->>DeviceA: Enable Cross-Device Sync
    DeviceA->>Cloud: Sync Settings
    Cloud-->>DeviceB: Sync Data
    DeviceB-->>User: Sync Complete